x4freetext: -SCATTERING OF SLOW NEUTRONS BY ARSENIC AND
FRM IS AN OPEN POOL REACTOR
WITH A THERMAL POWER OF 4 MEGAWATT.
OF SELENIUM, OF ORDINARY SELENIUM AND OF AS(2)-O(3).
EXHAUSTIVE DETAILS OF THESE SAMPLES ARE GIVEN IN
SCATTERING DENSITY OF A POWDERED SAMPLE WITH THAT
OF A RANGE OF LIQUID MIXTURES OF VARIED BUT WELL
KNOWN SCATTERING DENSITY. FOR COHERENT SCATTERING
SCATTERED NEUTRONS FROM THE CHRISTIANSEN FILTER.
DATE and several errors are corrected - SM
